<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Welcome to Design Net Inc</title>
  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Arial, sans-serif;
      background: linear-gradient(120deg, #082032, #334756 70%);
      color: #fff;
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
    }
    header {
      background: rgba(0,0,0,0.7);
      padding: 2rem 0;
      text-align: center;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
    }
    header h1 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 2.8rem;
      letter-spacing: 2px;
    }
    header p {
      margin-top: 0.5rem;
      font-size: 1.25rem;
      color: #ECDBBA;
    }
    main {
      flex: 1;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      padding: 2rem;
    }
    .welcome-box {
      background: rgba(51, 71, 86, 0.85);
      border-radius: 16px;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 16px rgba(0,0,0,0.12);
      max-width: 500px;
      padding: 2rem;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .welcome-box h2 {
      margin-top: 0;
      color: #F05454;
      font-size: 2rem;
    }
    .welcome-box p {
      color: #ECDBBA;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      margin: 1.5rem 0 0;
    }
    footer {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 1rem 0;
      background: rgba(0,0,0,0.6);
      color: #bbb;
      font-size: 1rem;
      letter-spacing: 1px;
    }
    @media (max-width: 600px) {
      .welcome-box {
        padding: 1rem;
      }
      header h1 {
        font-size: 2rem;
      }
      .welcome-box h2 {
        font-size: 1.4rem;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <header>
    <h1>Design Net Inc</h1>
    <p>Innovating Digital Experiences</p>
  </header>
  <main>
    <div class="welcome-box">
      <h2>Welcome!</h2>
      <p>
        We are <strong>Design Net Inc</strong>, a team passionate about crafting seamless digital solutions.<br><br>
        Explore our services, portfolio, and more as we bring your ideas to life with creativity and technology.<br>
        <br>
        <a href="mailto:contact@designnetinc.com" style="color: #F05454; text-decoration: underline;">Contact Us</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </main>
  <footer>
    &copy; 2025 Design Net Inc &mdash; All rights reserved.
  </footer>
</body>
</html>
